data.description: This stunning home is a must see! Located in a gated community. It boasts fantastic curb appeal with manicured- landscaping. Inside, you'll find a spacious 2 story foyer that leads to an open floor plan with a 2-story family room with columns that adds to the grandeur. Spacious Dining room with an open and inviting layout, it provides plenty of space for large dining table.  Gourmet kitchen with Stainless appliances, elegant Granite countertops with undermount sink. The owner's suite is huge with a luxurious glass shower, separate vanities, and an enormous walk-in closet. With this 4 bedroom, 3 full baths, and a powder room, this home offers plenty of space for your family. Conveniently situated near major highways, the Eagles Landing Country Club, eateries, banks, and grocery stores, this home won't last long on the market. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beauty your own!
